# Plan Adherence

- Follow the active numbered stage and accepted technical plan unless the user changes scope.
- Surface scope drift when touching files outside the active workflow/module/docs/CI surfaces.
- For new workflow work, keep requirements, tech plan, build, verification, docs, and memory-bank in sync.
- Do not skip verification gates silently; record skipped checks and reasons.
